org.hps.monitoring.ecal.eventdisplay.ui

Class CrystalFilterPanel.CDSComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.monitoring.ecal.eventdisplay.ui.CrystalFilterPanel.CDSComparator
  • Enclosing class:
    CrystalFilterPanel

    private class CrystalFilterPanel.CDSComparator
extends Object
    Class CDSComparator allows a set of filters for each property in a CrystalDataSet to be defined. It then will check to see if a given CrystalDataSet object matches the CDSComparator properties.
